original_title: Sinéad O'Connor: The Year Of The Horse
overview: Recorded live at "Forest National", Brussels (Belgium), on 29th October 1990 and "Ahoy Sport Paleis", Rotterdam (Netherlands), on 30th October 1990.  Tracklist  1	Feel So Different	6:19  2	The Emperor's New Clothes	4:41  3	I Want Your (Hands On Me)	4:14  4	Three Babies	4:58  5	Black Boys On Mopeds	3:40  6	Irish Ways	3:59  7	I Am Stretched On Your Grave	5:01  8	The Last Day Of Our Acquaintance	5:50  9	Nothing Compares 2 U	5:45  10	Jump In The River	5:15  11	Jerusalem	4:16  12	Troy	6:06
tagline: Sophie Muller's 67-minute concert film Year of the Horse is drawn from Sinéad O'Connor performances in Brussels and Rotterdam in October 1990.
title: Sinéad O'Connor: The Year Of The Horse
